name: Dinasor
description:
I am Dinasor, I am 100% organic inside and out!

Animals are organic cotton toys, stuffed animals made from natural materials and non-synthetic dyes, which are inspired by kids' imaginations and made for the world that our children will one day inherit. Though they are currently only being sold to retailers in bulk orders only, the web store for purchasing individual Aminals will be up soon, and if you're interested, you can contact us for more information.

These organic kids toys are inspired by the squiggly lines, bright colors, and purely unfettered, often hilarious drawings of young kids. With favorite animals and family members represented by unique natural organic toys, Aminals embody the collective imagination of young children well, while providing plenty of individual choices.
